                                    "content": "Pre-built shadcn/ui components are displayed with copy-paste code snippets. Each component is fully typed, WCAG-accessible, and Tailwind-customizable. The inspiration feed aggregates curated design content from multiple sources."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
